OL,4,CEx-reality TV stars' 'misleading' debt
OL,5,Cads banned
OL,6, Instagram posts by three reality TV
OL,7, stars promising that people in
OL,8, financial trouble could wipe out 85% of
OL,9, their debt have been banned.
OL,11,FThe ads were labelled "misleading" by
OL,12,Fthe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,13,F(ASA) for failing to highlight risks.
OL,15,FThe ASA said the ads over-simplified
OL,16,Fthe application process.
OL,18,FIt also said the posts by the three
OL,19,Fpeople, who have more than 4.5 million
OL,20,FInstagram followers between them,
OL,21,Fshould have been labelled as ads.
